86Mj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recUn6eVJDoG4xI0j","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"rechszjphdueUPvPi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recCkaxQ22JmTMMcU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"receagvMif63k28fg","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recM4YMG9qAp6yLP1","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recMNg0pz95anDnCU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"rec5DyQDXpkG4OiFl","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recabsaJkxxtgdUSt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recbaKaeB0APyZYLy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recoMMN7G2f7qaQuj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recwed5JcMZTCbdk1","target":"recQ1bj3p4Lj5MYY6","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec3qQg8n97ovgoVl","ref":"Isa.15.1","text":"The burden of Moab. Because in the night Ar of Moab is laid waste, and brought to silence; because in the night Kir of Moab is laid waste, and brought to silence;","year":-726},{"id":"recStbvLGV73b1V46","ref":"Isa.15.2","text":"He is gone up to Bajith, and to Dibon, the high places, to weep: Moab shall howl over Nebo, and over Medeba: on all their heads shall be baldness, and every beard cut off.","year":-726},{"id":"receqQmS9gF2g2HY2","ref":"Isa.15.3","text":"In their streets they shall gird themselves with sackcloth: on the tops of their houses, and in their streets, every one shall howl, weeping abundantly.","year":-726},{"id":"recDjhLpxMx4Q3Pzk","ref":"Isa.15.4","text":"And Heshbon shall cry, and Elealeh: their voice shall be heard even unto Jahaz: therefore the armed soldiers of Moab shall cry out; his life shall be grievous unto him.","year":-726},{"id":"receXTY4OSmwAYiEa","ref":"Isa.15.5","text":"My heart shall cry out for Moab; his fugitives shall flee unto Zoar, an heifer of three years old: for by the mounting up of Luhith with weeping shall they go it up; for in the way of Horonaim they shall raise up a cry of destruction.","year":-726},{"id":"recWn9wUZjbSMtTqg","ref":"Isa.15.6","text":"For the waters of Nimrim shall be desolate: for the hay is withered away, the grass faileth, there is no green thing.","year":-726},{"id":"rectXN7xyvydhqmGv","ref":"Isa.15.7","text":"Therefore the abundance they have gotten, and that which they have laid up, shall they carry away to the brook of the willows.","year":-726},{"id":"recRUpg0VQuCixyA9","ref":"Isa.15.8","text":"For the cry is gone round about the borders of Moab; the howling thereof unto Eglaim, and the howling thereof unto Beerelim.","year":-726}]}
